Package: chunkchecker
Title: Static Validator for R Code Chunks
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Santiago", "Lopez", role = c("aut", "cre"),
    email = "santiago.lopez.begines@gmail.com")
Description: RStudio addin that validates a selected R code chunk for
    syntax errors, undefined variables, bad function argument names,
    invalid file paths, and missing checkpoint files.
